Package com.example.fire_and_based

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.example.fire_and_based.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class User extends Object implements android.os.Parcelable
Represents a user in the application, including their personal information and events they are associated with. Implements Parcelable to enable passing User objects between activities.
